  <h1>Greenkeeper Style Guide</h1>
  <p>These are the design guidelines and resources for Greenkeeper.</p>
  <h2>Basics</h2>
  <h3>Colours</h3>
  <p>Greenkeeper has two basic colours, green for the hosted SaaS product, blue for the self-hosted enterprise product.</p>
