  <h3>Fonts</h3>
  <p>Our headline and logotype font is <strong>Futura</strong>. For headlines on the website we use Futura PT in 500 weight from TypeKit. The body text font stack is <code>Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif</code>, and for monospaced type, such as in code examples, we simply rely on <code>font-family: monospaced;</code>.</p>
